Lady Sun - '''Khorshid Khanom''' - is a character in many artistic and cultural practices and settings. [[Sun]], was the symbol of an aperture which divine light was flowing through it on earth. The sun with face of a beautiful Iranian lady with big captivating eyes and unibrows, probably as a symbol for beauty of [[goddess]]. Her image can be found in paintings, [[Screen printing|fabric printing]], [[Repoussé and chasing|embossed metal]], [[mirrors]], [[crockery|crockeries]], [[ceramics]] and much more.

